conversations.name: Utilities Chatbots
conversations.text: In utilities and energy, chatbots are typically used to automate customer service, provide step-by-step tutorials, and deliver information to keep customers safe.

conversations.name: Insurance Chatbot
conversations.text: Within insurance, chatbots are typically used to file claims, generate quotes, and answer basic policy and billing questions.

conversations.name: Govt Chatbot
conversations.when: government chatbot, federal chatbot, state chatbot
conversations.text: In government, chatbots are typically used to automate customer service and increase citizen engagement.

conversations.name: Healthcare Chatbot
conversations.text: In healthcare, chatbots are typically used to automate customer service, make it easier to refill prescriptions, and reduce patient readmission with reminders/instructions to help them stay healthy.

conversations.name: Financial Chatbots
conversations.text: In financial services, chatbots are typically used to automate customer service, automate collection of funds, and advise internal agents to help them deliver correct answers to customers in a more expedient manner.

conversations.name: Retail Chatbot
conversations.text: In retail, chatbots are typically used to provide status updates on orders, answer FAQs, and help with post-sales tasks such as recommending additional products or services.

conversations.name: Telco Chatbot
conversations.text: In telco, chatbots are typically used to automate customer service, automate upsell or cross-promotion, and provide technical support with interactive, step-by-step guides for setting up new devices.

conversations.name: Other Chatbots
